Package RestaurantSim

Class Cook

java.lang.Object
RestaurantSim.Cook
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITickableActionObject
public class Cook
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITickableActionObject
This class resembles a cook that is able to make an requested Order into a PreparedOrder. Time in which the order will be prepared depends solely on cook's agility and the quality of the prepared order can depend on a cook's skill level but any implementation IOrderQualityDeterminer passed to this class constructor can provide its own way to determine the quality of the PreparedOrder.
See Also:
QualityBasedOrderRater
